						               													<description>Get everyone on set and get rolling with this fun family game for movie buffs! Lights, Camera, Action is the ultimate movie themed party game where players have to draw, hum, mime and describe their way to Hollywood stardom! The perfect game for film fans, Lights, Camera, Action puts your movie knowledge to the ultimate test. Players pick a card featuring a famous film, then roll the die to determine the challenge. Depending on the result of the die, players then have to either ask trivia, hum, draw, mime or describe the film to the other players. So maybe your movie trivia is pretty good, but what about your drawing or miming skills? Lights, Camera, Action comes packaged in a neat clapperboard style box and includes 50 question cards, a notepad, pencil, sand timer and custom die. A great game to enjoy with friends or family, Lights, Camera, Action is a fun, fast paced movie quiz game that gets a little more from its star performers!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
